{"tid":293274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[花生品牌代理] 女童玩「矇眼猜猜樂」　竟被狼師逼口交","createTime":"2017-06-22T04:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T17:43:34.000Z","uid":27324,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f1f60f46669af02bcaee3230a86031601f5c05","tid":293274,"uid":27324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:37:20.000Z","msg":"屌 根本就係花生品牌代理d 故黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>女童玩「矇眼猜猜樂」　竟被狼師逼口交</strong><br />\n<br />\n北市1名在幼稚園擔任代課老師的康姓男子，2015年於某國小附設幼兒園任教時，竟利用與一名5歲女童獨處機會，誆騙要玩「矇眼猜猜樂」遊戲，用口罩遮住女童眼睛，逼迫女童幫他口交，還問女童：「妳猜猜看這是什麼？」直到女童和媽媽聊天時，說出「康老師有叫我舔他的隱私處」，全案才爆發。雖康男否認犯罪，但士林地院審理後，有證人證稱，曾目睹他抱著睡著的女童自慰，再加上女童女童指證歷歷，依加重強制性交罪判他8年有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20170622/1145075/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flocal%2F20170622%2F1145075%2F&d=17n4cqxg%2B2J6khD3gA7q%2BAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=31666571\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20170622/1145075/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">插！</span></span>"},{"pid":"59af54f32a20a00327621d90bddf94eda65ec913","tid":293274,"uid":23876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:41:01.000Z","msg":"北市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0486d57dcb71f591223d6e93f65294bfadb782","tid":293274,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c4d8afa2f28c1d8bf53d91482d5106ed28ff9bd","tid":293274,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"北市+1"},{"pid":"6d4e15b88fdc27c8d1e22cb203b2c5c8cab17185","tid":293274,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply